However, none of the .avi files will play.  They all come up as being corrupted in any player I use.  Can you not play the files as they finish?  Or do I need to wait until the entire download is completed before any of the individual files will work?

Thanks for any help.
King, you'll have to wait until it's completely downloaded.

Shute, thank you very much!  I was afraid that I was doing something wrong and didn't want to be uploading corrupted files to others.

BitTorrent downloads random fragments from the files who in the end comes together as one (or more) file(s). That's you'll have to wait until it's 100% done.
